Revision history for ddstartup

0.04 2026-04-28
    - changed install-time auto-setup to skip cleanly on unsupported hosts
    - kept explicit ddstartup systemd commands strict when systemctl is unavailable

0.03 2026-04-28
    - fixed generated systemd units to preserve the active Perl runtime library path
    - made dashboard ddstartup.setup derive PERL5LIB from the running Perl @INC when the environment variable is unset

0.02 2026-04-28
    - changed ddstartup commands to print pretty table output by default
    - added -o json support across setup, enable, disable, status, logs, and remove

0.01 2026-04-28
    - created the ddstartup skill to manage systemd startup for Developer Dashboard
    - added setup, status, logs, and remove commands for systemctl and journalctl
    - verified the skill in Docker with 100% coverage
